Class EmployeeRepository

java.lang.Object
com.itesm.AmazonRHS.Equipo4DB.Repositories.EmployeeRepository
@Repository public class EmployeeRepository extends Object
EmployeeRepository is a class dedicated to read and write data from the table Employee on DynamoDB.
